name: SanDiegoBorder
0:
”Alexa, open San Diego Border”
”Alexa, ask San Diego Border how many cars are in San Ysidro”
”Alexa, ask San Diego Border how many cars are in Otay”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: san diego border
des:
Plan ahead when crossing the Tijuana/San Diego border by asking Alexa how many cars and pedestrians are at the San Ysidro and Otay Mesa ports of entry. You can ask for both ports, or an specific one. 
Alexa will tell you how many doors are open, how many cars are in the normal, ready lane, sentri, and pedestrian lanes. 

(Information is gathered from CBP. The developer is not responsible for the information given. Wait times may vary.)
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
